prod.desciption:
Jordan Brand kept it classic with the Jordan 1 Low Gym Red White. This colorway draws inspiration from the highly coveted New Beginnings Pack Air Jordan 1 High that was released in February of 2020.

This Jordan 1 Low is composed of a white leather upper with red overlays. A red Nike Swoosh, white midsole, and red outsole complete the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $90.
